  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d740d",
      "text": "Hatena2010-09-16",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d740e",
      "text": "code:hatena",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d740f",
      "text": " <body>",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7410",
      "text": " *1284638475*genkoに脚注機能をつけよう",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7411",
      "text": " <a href='http://d.hatena.ne.jp/nishiohirokazu/20100911/1284167528'>HTMLで雑誌の原稿を書くためのツール</a>で原稿を書いている。脚注を本文中に書きたいけど、見るときには本文中には(*)とか出して、脚注の本体は本文とは別のところに出したい。",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7412",
      "text": " >||",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7413",
      "text": " <a class=\"footnote\">(脚注: ほげほげ)<;/a>",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7414",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7415",
      "text": " と書くと本文としては(*)になってくれて、僕のCSS力では脚注・傍注として表示するのは難しいので、とりあえずクリックしたらalertで出すようにしようと思った。",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7416",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7417",
      "text": " これがそのコード",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7418",
      "text": " >|javascript|",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7419",
      "text": "     // 脚注span.footnoteを(*)で表現",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d741a",
      "text": "     $(\".footnote\").each(function(){",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d741b",
      "text": " \tvar text = this.innerHTML;",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d741c",
      "text": " \tthis.innerHTML = \"(*)\"",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d741d",
      "text": " \tthis.href = \"#\";",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d741e",
      "text": " \t$(this).click(function(){",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d741f",
      "text": " \t    alert(text);",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7420",
      "text": " \t});",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7421",
      "text": "     });",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7422",
      "text": " ||<",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7423",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7424",
      "text": " だけどクリックしてもalertがでないんだよな。何がいけないんだろう？",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7425",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7426",
      "text": " <hr>",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7427",
      "text": " ",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7428",
      "text": " ああ、わかった、hrを本文の裏に入れたくて#containerでz-index: -2、hrでz-index: -1とかやっていたのがいけないようだ。これは親エレメントの値からの相対値で、これだとhrが-3になってしまう。あと負の値にはあまりしないようだ。多分これが原因でclickイベントをbodyとかが受け取ってしまってたんだろう。コンテナでz-index: 2をしてhrでz-index: -1したら期待通りの挙動になった。",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec29aff09e00003d7429",
      "text": " </body>",
      "created": 1284562800,
      "updated": 1284562800,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
